1 2 3 4@Switch tabs (Repos / Sessions / Teams / Fleet)
.TE
.SS Table Navigation
.TS
tab(@);
l l.
j / ↓@Move cursor down
k / ↑@Move cursor up
Enter@Drill into selected item
s@Cycle sort column
Space@Toggle selection
.TE
.SS Repo Actions (Repos tab and Repo Detail)
.TS
tab(@);
l l.
S@Start loop
X@Stop loop / session
P@Pause / resume loop
a@Actions menu
